snippet.title: ExposingSMG
snippet.description:
Exposing the inside world of Hollywood and reporting pop culture news one video or blog post at a time. This channel will often report what mainstream media doesn't want to report. Come hang out with us in the comments and listen to some new tea!

Your favorite bloggers,
Angela & Alana ;)
